metadata.name: Cloudbox
metadata.description:
Sandbox or Cloudbox?

━

Yeah that's the dream I had as a kid, I've been fascinated by the clouds from young age, one day I was I looking up to the sky Imagining myself flying through the clouds, and the same night is when I had a dream of me playing in a room full of clouds, that's when, Cloudman was born in my mind.

━

The first auction winner will get exclusive package!
That Includes: I will personally print the poster of artwork with the barcode of the token and sign an autograph and ship it to the winner. Custom artwork I'll try to recreate your dream.

━

2400 x 3000 px
